      >
        <!-- <p class="text-sm pb-4">
           This mug will keep your drinks at the perfect temperature... so you can stay at your desk and keep working.
        </p> -->

        <!-- <p class="text-sm pb-4">Like you, this mug is "Smart".<br />You're smart like mug.</p> -->
        <p class="text-sm pb-4">
          (See Sherry to collect)
